gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.veritesting

Class FixedPointWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.veritesting.FixedPointWrapper

  • public class FixedPointWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is called multiple times over different transformations. What it does is that it keeps a common state among all transformations, that is was called on.
